OL,3,CGreggs launches chicken version of
OL,4,Csausage and vegan rolls in 'iconic
OL,5,Ctrilogy'
OL,7,FGreggs is launching a chicken version
OL,8,Fof its customer favourite sausage and
OL,9,Fvegan rolls in a permanent addition to
OL,10,Fits menu.
OL,12,FThe Chicken Roll ` described by the
OL,13,Fhigh street baker as "seasoned chicken
OL,14,Fwrapped in layers of crisp, golden,
OL,15,Fglazed puff pastry" contains 305
OL,16,Fcalories and will cost #1.35 when it
OL,17,Fgoes on sale on Thursday.
OL,19,FIt follows the Sausage Roll and the
OL,20,Fpork free Vegan Roll.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
