OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775552356
OL,3,CGreggs launches chicken version of
OL,4,Csausage and vegan rolls in 'iconic
OL,5,Ctrilogy'
OL,7,FTo celebrate the final launch of the
OL,8,F"trilogy", Greggs is allowing
OL,9,Fcustomers the chance to be among the
OL,10,Ffirst to taste the new roll with a 20-
OL,11,Fminute slot between 3.30pm and 9pm on
OL,12,FWednesday (8) at a pop-up location at
OL,13,F15 Bateman Street, in London's Soho.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775552356
OL,3,CGreggs launches chicken version of
OL,4,Csausage and vegan rolls in 'iconic
OL,5,Ctrilogy'
OL,7,FPlaces will be given on a first-come
OL,8,Ffirst-served basis but, in a nod to
OL,9,Fthe trilogy theme, guests must arrive
OL,10,Fas part of a trio of friends or family.
OL,12,FVisitors will be able to pair their
OL,13,Fthree complimentary rolls with a free
OL,14,Fchicken-themed cocktail or mocktail.
OL,16,FA Greggs spokeswoman said: "They say
OL,17,Fthe best things come in threes, and
OL,18,Four iconic roll trilogy is no
OL,19,Fexception.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
