PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775552356
OL,3,CGreggs launches chicken version of
OL,4,Csausage and vegan rolls in 'iconic
OL,5,Ctrilogy'
OL,7,F"We can't wait for our customers to
OL,8,Fexperience the Chicken Roll as the
OL,9,Fultimate headline act of our flaky
OL,10,Ffranchise."
OL,12,FOver the past year, Greggs has come
OL,13,Funder pressure from cautious shoppers
OL,14,Faffected by the rising cost of living,
OL,15,Fhigher tax and labour costs, and the
OL,16,Fgrowing use of weight-loss treatments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
