OL,3,CGreggs launches chicken version of
OL,4,Csausage and vegan rolls in 'iconic
OL,5,Ctrilogy'
OL,7,FLast month, the Newcastle-based firm
OL,8,Freported that statutory pre-tax
OL,9,Fprofits fell by 17.9% to #167.4
OL,10,Fmillion for the year to December 27,
OL,11,Fcompared with a year earlier.
OL,13,FIt also told shareholders that total
OL,14,Fsales grew by 6.8% to #2.15 billion
OL,15,Fover the year, with like-for-like
OL,16,Fgrowth buoyed by its continued store
OL,17,Fopening programme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
