OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775552356
OL,3,CGreggs launches chicken version of
OL,4,Csausage and vegan rolls in 'iconic
OL,5,Ctrilogy'
OL,7,FGreggs said it had 121 net store
OL,8,Fopenings in 2025, expanding its shop
OL,9,Festate to 2,739 locations by the end
OL,10,Fof the year.
OL,12,FIt is targeting around 120 further
OL,13,Fopenings this year as it highlighted
OL,14,Fambitions to grow to "significantly
OL,15,Fmore than 3,000 UK shops over longer
OL,16,Fterm".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
